OL,5, The BBC has paid a "substantial sum" in
OL,6, damages to the former private secretary
OL,7, of Diana, Princess of Wales, for the   
OL,8, "harm caused to him" over Martin       
OL,9, Bashir's Panorama interview.           
OL,11,FThe corporation said it had apologised 
OL,12,Funreservedly to Patrick Jephson and had
OL,13,Fpaid his legal costs.                  
OL,15,FThe 1995 interview was subject to an   
OL,16,Finvestigation that found Mr Bashir used
OL,17,Ffake documents to gain access to Diana.
OL,19,FMr Jephson intends to donate the money 
OL,20,Fto UK charities, the BBC said.         
